Service  on  a  minor  is  accomplished  by  serving  the  
parent, or guardian, or if none can be located after 
reasonable efforts, any other person having care or 
control  of  the  minor,  or  with  whom  the  minor  
resides,  or  by  whom  the  minor  is  employed.  If  the  
minor  is  12  or  over,  an  additional  copy  must  be  
served on the minor. (
