c. Service of Custody or Visitation Motions 
The  LCSA  is  generally  not  required  to  serve  or  
receive  service  of  papers,  pleadings,  or  documents  
relating to issues of custody or visitation, nor is the 
LCSA  generally  required  to  attend  any  hearing  or  
