previously  established  father  is  not  the  genetic  
father, specific reasons for this belief and a request 
that relief be granted, and 
d. A  declaration  that  the  marital  presumption  of  
FC  §  7540  does  not  apply  and  that  the  action  is  
not barred by 
FC § 7630(a)(2). 
5. Venue 
The motion must be filed in a    court of proper venue. 
(
FC § 7647(a)(1)). 
6. Service  of  the Motion 
The  motion  must  be  served  on  the  parties  to  the  
action   resulting   in   the   judgment   of   parentage   
including any involved LCSA. (
FC § 7647.5). 
