82 
 
 
 PRACTICE  POINT:  SSI  benefits  are  exempt  and 
paid on  the  1
st 
of  the  month.  Verify  the  payment  date 
on award letters   or   payment   stubs   to   determine 
whether  or  not  the  benefits  are  exempt  as  income  or 
from enforcement. 
 
 PRACTICE  POINT: Mandatory  motion  to  modify  
support   is   required   within   30   days   of   receipt   of   
