filed,  it  has  the  same  force,  effect  and  priority  as  a  
personal  property  judgment  lien.  The  judgment  lien  
continues for five years unless a   continuation statement 
is timely filed. (CCP § 697.510(b)). 
Q. VETERAN’S BENEFITS  
A    former    military    service    member    may    receive    
payments  from  the  branch  of  the  armed  service  for  
which    service    was    provided    and/or    from    the    
