earn them payments from their branch of   service 
as opposed to the VA. This is  treated the same as 
“regular”  military  retirement  (can be  garnished, 
is taxable, etc.) (
10 USC § 3911, 10 USC §   6323, 
10 USC §   8911, 10 USC § 1201, 10 USC §   1202, 
and 
10 USC §  1401). 
