3. Installment  Judgment 
Only the initial support order shall be considered an 
installment  judgment;  no  order  setting  forth  the  
amount of   support owed for prior periods of time or 
establishing   periodic   payments   to   liquidate   the   
arrears shall be considered a   money judgment. (
