,  as amended in 2002) 
4. Bankruptcy 
Interest  on  child  support  debt  (including  welfare  
arrears)   continues   to   accrue   after   a   Chapter   13   
petition   is   filed   and   is   non-dischargeable   and   
collectable,  even  after  discharge  and  even  if  not  
requested in the Plan or   Proof of   Claim. (
In re Foster 
(9th Cir. 2003) 319 F.3d 495). 
5. Military 
A servicemember may request a 6% interest rate on 
pre-service  debts  pursuant  to  the  Servicemember’s  
Civil  Relief  Act  (SCRA)  (See at 
50  USCA  § 3937.) 
(See also Section XV.C.7 –   Military). 
