Any  party  may  request  a  judicial  determination  of  
arrears.  (
FC  §  17526).  The  motion  shall   include   a   
monthly  breakdown  showing  amounts  ordered  and  
amounts paid. A court order determining arrears is res 
judicata  and  cannot  be  re-litigated  (as  to  that  time  
period).  (See 
Wodicka  v.  Wodicka  (1976)  17  Cal.3d  
181, 188) 
