indemnity has been paid, an injured worker can 
request  that  the  ongoing  or  future  medical  care  
be  quantified  into  a  lump-sum  payment.  (LC  §  
5100). While a  defendant insurance carrier is not 
required to  settle out the future medical care, it is 
often an advantage to do so to reduce its future',
