order, decision, or directive, whether temporary 
or  final,  or  subject  to  modification,  issued  in  a  
state or foreign country for the benefit of a   child, 
a   spouse, or   a former spouse providing monetary 
support,   health   care,   arrearages,   retroactive   
support, or reimbursement. (
FC § 5700.102(28)).',
