a. Use  of  tribal  customs  or  common  law  (45 
CFR § 309.90(b)); 
b. Tribes are not required to adopt UIFSA but are 
required   to   recognize   child   support   orders   
issued by other jurisdictions in accordance with 
FFCCSOA (
45 CFR § 309.120(b)); 
c. In-kind  support  (non-cash)  may  be  allowed,  
but  must  have  cash  equivalency  and  cannot  be  
