  'CSDA CHILD SUPPORT ATTORNEY SOURCEBOOK 2024 
268 
 
 
attempt  to  resolve  any  procedural  issues  by  
communicating  with  the  tribal  court  judge,  
provided the parties are given the opportunity 
to  participate  in  all  communications  and  a  
