The SCRA also allows the servicemember to obtain a 
temporary stay of   the proceedings if  the individual’s 
circumstances warrant. 
a. Initial Mandatory Stay 
Pursuant  to  
50  USC  §  3931(d),  the  court  must  
grant a stay for at least 90 days upon application 
of  counsel,  or  on  the  court’s  own  motion,  if  the  
