income and deductions. 
C. FORM 1040:   OVERVIEW                 
Form 1040, which U.S. taxpayers use to file an annual 
individual  income  tax  return,  is  the  tax  return  that  
the LCSA attorney will most commonly review. The 
1040 was redesigned effective tax year 2022 and has 
been improved to categorize and identify sources of 
income. The IRS has also released a new alternative 
