income,   taxable   income,   W-2 wages paid   by   the 
business,  unadjusted  basis  of    qualified  property  and 
whether the business is a   qualified or   specified business. 
See the QBI deduction calculator at 
https://childsupport.ca.gov/calculate-child-support/ 
when  IRS  Form  1040  is  not  available  to  determine  the',
