Notice  to  Appear  and  Produce  when  generated.  If 
you  wish  to  keep  a  copy  for  reference  or  potential  
later  use,  you  will  need  to  upload  an  image  of  the  
Notice when you issue it. 
3. Exceptions  to   Live  Testimony  Requirement 
a. Stipulation of   the parties; and 
b. “In appropriate  cases,  a  court  may  make  a 
finding  of  good cause  to   refuse  to   receive  live 
